## Transform Android UI with **LoadingIndicator**, **SplitButtonLayout**, and **ButtonGroup**
[](https://medium.com/@stefanoq21?source=post_page---byline--9ea77959a262---------------------------------------)[Stefano Natali](https://medium.com/@stefanoq21?source=post_page---byline--9ea77959a262---------------------------------------)Follow7 min readMay 20, 2025[
